ut areas are experiencing issues at the moment. Please try again later.","EMERGENCY_MESSAGE_GENERAL":"Some things might not work as they should. This could be due to maintenance or another issue. Please check back in a few hours.","EMERGENCY_MESSAGE_LIMITED_RANGE_BUYABILITY":"Some parts of our range are currently unavailable online. Please try again later. Still unavailable? Browse the range for a similar item.","EMERGENCY_MESSAGE_LOGIN":"It’s not possible to log in at the moment. Please continue to shop as a guest.","EMERGENCY_MESSAGE_STORE_CHECKOUT":"Our in-store checkout is currently not working. In the meantime, you can shop and pay online.","ERROR_404_BODY_HTML":"<p>The page you are looking for can't be found.</p><p>Maybe the links below can be helpful.</p>","ERROR_404_GO_ELSEWHERE":"Let's bounce you back to somewhere more inspiring.","ERROR_404_HEADING":"Oops! Something went wrong :(","ERROR_404_TITLE":"Page can't be found","ERROR_404_TO_HOMEPAGE":"hop on over to the homepage.","ERROR_404_USE_SEARCH_OR":"Search to find what you're looking for, or","ERROR_500_BACK_TO_HOMEPAGE":"Go back to the IKEA homepage","ERROR_500_HEADING":"It seems our servers are in trouble. Sorry!","FLOATING_ACTION_BUTTON_ACCESSIBLE_LABEL":"Floating action buttons","FOOTER_ACCESSIBLE_HEADING":"Footer","FOOTER_TEXT":"© Inter IKEA Systems B.V. 2000-{{currentYear}}","HEJ_FIRST_NAME":"Hej {{firstName}}!","HEJ_LOGIN_SIGN_UP":"Hej! Log in","HEJ_NEUTRAL_GREETING":"Hej!","HOME":"Home","IKEA_LOGO_ACCESSIBLE_LABEL":"IKEA Home","LOCALISATION_CANCEL_MODAL":"Cancel","LOCALISATION_CHANGE_COUNTRY_DISCLAIMER":"Your shopping bag will empty if you change to a different country/region.","LOCALISATION_CHANGE_COUNTRY_LINK":"Change country/region","LOCALISATION_CURRENT_STORE_HEADING":"You're in the India online store","LOCALISATION_SELECT_LANGUAGE":"Select your preferred language","LOCATION_OPEN_24H":"Open 24 hours","LOCATION_OPEN_TODAY":"Open today {{from - to}}","LOCATION_OPEN_TODAY_24H":"Open 24 hours toda